    <string name="installed_via_fdroid_appnyoure_all_set">✅ Installed via F-Droid app?\nYou\'re all set! Just follow the accessibility setup in the next step.\n\n⚠️ Downloaded from F-Droid website?\nPlease install through the F-Droid app instead to avoid permission issues.</string>
    <string name="apk_installation">APK Installation</string>
    <string name="if_you_installed_from_an_apk">If you installed from an APK, follow these steps:\n\n1️⃣ Open Settings → Apps → Curbox\n\n2️⃣ Tap Permissions → Special App Access → Accessibility → Enable Curbox\n\n3️⃣ Return to Curbox App Info → Scroll down → Tap Restricted Settings → Allow\n\n💡 Pro tip: Install via F-Droid app for a smoother setup! 🚀</string>
